      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited for a dedicated project or as a comprehensive parts donor. The engine currently runs very roughly and will require major mechanical overhaul to be roadworthy again. Additionally, the body shows significant wear, including noticeable rust patches and faded paint, while the interior requires a complete restoration due to heavy staining and upholstery damage. We are offering it at a low price to account for the extensive work needed.",
