      "description": "Used vehicle in good condition. Clean title. Maintenance records available. Recent oil change and tire rotation. Minor exterior scratches. Runs smooth.",
      "price": 28500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
