    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained vehicle that perfectly balances performance and practicality. The exterior finish remains vibrant and glossy, though close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear passenger-side wheel arch\u2014typical for a well-loved daily driver. Inside, the cabin is remarkably clean and has never been smoked in. The leather upholstery is free of tears or punctures, showing only light, natural creasing on the driver's bolster. All onboard electronics, from the intuitive infotainment system to the dual-zone climate control, operate exactly as they should. Mechanically, this car is in great shape; it has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer's schedule, with a recent full synthetic oil change and a fresh set of brake pads installed just 2,000 miles ago. The engine runs quietly, the transmission shifts are crisp, and the suspension remains firm and responsive. This is a dependable, honest car ready for its next owner to drive away with confidence.",
      "price": 32450.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
